:

*Tokom* večeri rekao je nešto zanimljivo. (During the evening he said something interesting.) 

*Tokom* nastave učenici su se dobro zabavljali. (During the class the students had a good time.) 

*Tokom* mog detinjstva proputovao sam mnogo zemalja. (During my childhood I traveled to many countries.) 

*Tokom* dana sam provodio vreme u parku. (During the day I spent time in the park.) 

*Tokom* večere pričali smo o svojim planovima. (During the dinner we talked about our plans.)